<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>FAQ</title>
    <!-- CSS only -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <!-- JavaScript Bundle with Popper -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/views/css/faq.css" />
    {{!-- favicon --}}
    {{>favicon}}
</head>

<body>
    {{!-- Header --}}
    {{>header}}
    {{!-- /header --}}
    <h2 class="text-center m-2 mt-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="container mt-5 border border-light border-2 rounded-3 shadow">
        <div class="row">
            <!-- Question open 1 -->
            <p>
                <a class="btn btn-light mt-3 quesHover" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#Q1" role="button"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="Q1">
                    What is the Full form of HUMCARE ?
                </a>
            </p>
            <div class="collapse" id="Q1">
                <div class="card card-body bg-secondary text-light">
                    The Full Form of HUMCARE is "HUMAN CARE".
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Question close 1 -->
            <!-- Question open 2 -->
            <p>
                <a class="btn btn-light mt-3 quesHover" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#Q2" role="button"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="Q2">
                    What are the Documents Required for the Registration ?
                </a>
            </p>
            <div class="collapse" id="Q2">
                <div class="card card-body bg-secondary text-light">
                    The Basic Requirements are :
                    <ul>
                        <li>Mobile Number</li>
                        <li>AdharCard Number</li>
                        <li>or any Government Approved ID Card</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Question close 2 -->
            <!-- Question open 3 -->
            <p>
                <a class="btn btn-light mt-3 quesHover" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#Q3" role="button"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="Q3">
                    How Many Registrations are Possible with 1 Mobile Number ?
                </a>
            </p>
            <div class="collapse" id="Q3">
                <div class="card card-body bg-secondary text-light">
                    Any Number of Registation Can be Done
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Question close 3 -->
            <!-- Question open 4 -->
            <p>
                <a class="btn btn-light mt-3 quesHover" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#Q4" role="button"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="Q4">
                    Is online registration mandatory for Vaccination?
                </a>
            </p>
            <div class="collapse" id="Q4">
                <div class="card card-body bg-secondary text-light">
                    Yes Online Registration is Mandatory Because We are Accepting
                    Registeration Online Only.
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Question close 4 -->
            <!-- Question open 5 -->
            <p>
                <a class="btn btn-light mt-3 quesHover" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#Q5" role="button"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="Q5">
                    Is there any registration charge to be paid?
                </a>
            </p>
            <div class="collapse" id="Q5">
                <div class="card card-body bg-secondary text-light">
                    No, there is no registration charge. but Charges for Vaccination is
                    There.
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Question close 5 -->
            <!-- Question open 6 -->
            <p>
                <a class="btn btn-light mt-3 quesHover" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#Q6" role="button"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="Q6">
                    Can I register for vaccination without Aadhaar card?
                </a>
            </p>
            <div class="collapse" id="Q6">
                <div class="card card-body bg-secondary text-light">
                    Yes, if you are 18 years or older you Can Register with Following
                    IDs.
                    <ul>
                        <li>PAN CARD</li>
                        <li>Driving Licence</li>
                        <li>Voter ID</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Question close 6 -->
            <!-- Question open 7 -->
            <p>
                <a class="btn btn-light mt-3 quesHover" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#Q7" role="button"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="Q7">
                    From Where Do I get Vaccinated
                </a>
            </p>
            <div class="collapse" id="Q7">
                <div class="card card-body bg-secondary text-light">
                    Student can get Vaccinated from there particular Departments and
                    others from B1 Block.
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Question close 7 -->
            <!-- Question open 8 -->
            <p>
                <a class="btn btn-light mt-3 quesHover" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#Q8" role="button"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="Q8">
                    Is Vaccination Available on Saturday and Sunday ?
                </a>
            </p>
            <div class="collapse" id="Q8">
                <div class="card card-body bg-secondary text-light">
                    No, you can only be Vaccinated on Working days (i.e Monday to
                    Friday).
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Question close 8 -->
            <!-- Question open 9 -->
            <p>
                <a class="btn btn-light mt-3 quesHover" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#Q9" role="button"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="Q9">
                    What are the precautions be taken after Taking Vaccine ?
                </a>
            </p>
            <div class="collapse" id="Q9">
                <div class="card card-body bg-secondary text-light">
                    You Should take Rest and avoid junk Food. if You feel any Side
                    effects Contact Us or You can Approach nearest Doctor.
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Question close 9 -->
            <!-- Question open 10 -->
            <p>
                <a class="btn btn-light mt-3 quesHover" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#Q10" role="button"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="Q10">
                    What are the precautions be taken before Taking Vaccine ?
                </a>
            </p>
            <div class="collapse" id="Q10">
                <div class="card card-body bg-secondary text-light">
                    Before Vaccination you should take Proper Meal and avoid junk food.
                    and don't take any Kind of Medicine before Vaccination and if you
                    are suffering from any Disease then firstly Consult with Doctor.
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Question close 10 -->
        </div>
    </div>
    {{!-- footer --}}
    {{>footer}}
    {{!-- /footer --}}
</body>

</html>